Summary: I took this picture of the cliffs of the grand canyon and found this.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on vacation at the grand canyon and i took this picture of the cliffs, later when i looked at the photos on my computer i saw this funny looking object in the sky. I dont know what it is but it looks to me like a ufo, when i enhanced it on Kodak easyshare all i got were some messed up pixles. 1.We stoped to take pictures of the scenery at The grand canyon. 2.I first noticed the object when i loaded the pictures onto my computer. 3.I first thought it was a Ufo, but i thought it could have been a bug but it has no obveous wings and was too far in the distance. 4.It is green and looks like a missle, but i only saw it on the computer when i got home. 5.I didnt see it when i took the picture.
